selftests: net: rtnetlink.sh: add fdb get test

tests the below three cases of bridge fdb get:
[bridge, mac, vlan]
[bridge_port, mac, vlan, flags=[NTF_MASTER]]
[vxlandev, mac, flags=NTF_SELF]

depends on iproute2 support for bridge fdb get.

